lead_paragraph: Spaniard Maverick Vinales roared to his first MotoGP victory for Suzuki at Silverstone on Sunday with Britain's Cal Crutchlow second in his home race after starting on pole.

headline.print_headline: Motorcycling: Vinales Takes First MotoGP Win at Silverstone
headline.main: Motorcycling: Vinales Takes First MotoGP Win at Silverstone
